data.description: This cozy single-level home in SW Reno boasts excellent curb appeal, inviting you in from the moment you arrive. Situated on a cul-de-sac like circle, set back a bit from the street, with attractive, low-maintenance front landscaping adding to the allure. It is situated in a desirable area near walking trails, Bartley Ranch, and Huffaker Elementary, and the floor plan offers ample space for comfortable living. Recent upgrades include a newer HVAC system and flooring that enhances it's value and appeal.
